Take the hassle out of managing and scheduling your Instagram feed!

My Feed · Preview for Instagram is an app that automates and organizes your InstaLife. 
Our app offers you an EASY-TO-USE interface and tools built specifically to make your Instagram account a unique one. Select what types of images you want to share, and preview grid layouts to create a striking Instagram profile. 

THE MAIN FEATURE - you can preview not only the grid, but also the profile picture, captions, and highlight covers. Also:
- Save drafts
- Write your captions in advance and perfect them
- Create multiple versions of your account
- Drag drop to arrange the order of your posts
- Edit photos with filters

Our Planner for Instagram offers TOOLS to edit your images in the app, as well as some incredible fonts for your Bio and posts. Customize your feed by applying all these stunning tools to your account. Play around with the design of different themed grids before integrating them into your feed.

KEY FEATURES:
- Design, preview, and schedule grid layouts to create Insta feed;
- Upload images with no grid limits;
- Organize and edit Insta posts; 
- Add captions and perfect them;
- Create highlight covers;
- Drag-and-drop tool; 
- Incredible Insta fonts for Bio and posts;
- Push notification reminders.

Schedule your posts by setting a day and time. When it is time to upload photos, the Planner for Instagram will send you a push notification. All you need is to send your post to Instagram and paste your caption.

Instagram is more relevant now than ever before, use a My Feed to make the most of it.

